        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Taxpayer Penalty Protection Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill exempts taxpayers from penalties for failure to pay estimated income tax in taxable years beginning in 2020 if such taxpayers (1) paid at least 70% of the tax due for the current year, and (2) paid 70% (90% if adjusted gross income exceeds $150,000) of tax shown on returns for the prior year.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
